(Part 1 of 2) Raging controversies are swirling about whether current COVID vaccine mandates could be the biblical mark of the beast. Tim Saxton and Steve Wohlberg separate facts from fiction as they explain what the Holy Bible really says about the beast and the mark. https://www.whitehorsemedia.com/product/the-bloody-woman-and-the-seven-headed-beast/
